firstLocal: The First local cryptocurrency exchange in Iraq
registerYourPhone: Enter your mobile phone number to get the Nakhlex App download link.
benefitsHint: The one-stop Cryptocurrency platform in Iraq
benefitHint-1: Our Arabic and Kurdish clients could select their own languages for making trading easy to use both in App usage and support.
benefitHint-2: Authentication is under 30 minutes to make KYC process faster than ever to save our clients time.
benefitHint-3: Nakhlex has been designed to be simple than every other crypto trading platforms by providing the best user experience.
featuresHint: Nakhlex is the easiest, fastest and safest App in cryptocurrency based on the needs of people for buying and selling crypto in Iraq. Easily swap between main features and choose your suitable way of trading.
downloadNakhlexHint: A safe and easy to use cryptocurrency exchange along with your moments.
contactUsHint: Our mission is to facilitate infrastructure of cryptocurrency exchange and to provide freedom of trade in MENA region.

aboutUsHint: Our mission is to be the most reliable and knowledgeable cryptocurrency digital platform in Iraq. Our vision is to progress the methods of financial investment by spreading freedom of money in MENA region.
ourHistoryHint: The NAKHLEX team is made up of a group of Iraqi university graduates who specialize in a variety of fields, including computer programming, management and economic. The team has been active in buying and selling digital currencies for the past few years. During these years, we have observed lack of a local bilingual platform that needs to be fit with the culture and language of Iraqi people. In addition, access to foreign digital exchanges, selling and buying unfairly by domestic exchanges also, lack of a secure and professional platform for trading digital currencies are other difficulties in this context. For the aforesaid reasons we decided to create a completely secure, fast and easy-to-use, bilingual and simple platform in buying and selling digital currencies specifically for Iraqi people.
